Issues.Body:
### Background and motivation

The proposed API allows customers to drag, drop, copy and paste virtual files. Currently tasks like pasting files from remote desktop or dropping attachments from Outlook requires reflection to access the files (or rewrite the whole OLE infrastructure for data transfer).

PR #7738

